name: Into Rain (Unedited Original)
description: Into Rain was taken in a popular shopping center in the Harajuku district of Tokyo. By this point in the day, my rain jacket had become soaked through; I was on a mission to make it back to the comfort of that studio shelter. This installment, a two-story fractured mirror encompassing an escalator, honestly caught me off guard.
